en_202571_0	To be in line with the ongoing Presidential Task Force-initiated drug eradication drive, Mr Rasika Weerathunga, an Instructor at Sri Lanka Sumithuro Melmedura and Vista Counseling service delivered a lecture on 'Drug Prevention' and its international network, etc to the troops serving the Security Forces-West.
en_202571_1	It was held at 9 Battalion Sri Lanka Light Infantry (SLLI) premises on Thursday (27).
en_202571_2	Major General Sathyapriya Liyanage, Commander, Security Forces-West has directed the General Officer Commanding, 14 Division to organize the arrangement.
